OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers this evening, these dying out.
OL,7,FThen then the rest of the night will
OL,8,Fbe dry with clear periods. Cold with
OL,9,Fpatchy frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA mainly dry day, bright with
OL,12,Fsome hazy sunny intervals but in
OL,13,Fgeneral a lot of cloud, perhaps a spot
OL,14,For two of rain. Freshening southerly
OL,15,Fwind.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
