OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,6,Fdry and quite warm for much of
OL,7,FTuesday, cloudier later with showery
OL,8,Frain. Chance of patchy or rain or
OL,9,Fshowers on Wednesday. Sunshine and
OL,10,Fshowers on Thursday.
